{"tid":2122672,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"水務署一名承建商工人確診 屯門濾水廠全面消毒","createTime":"2020-07-24T06:35:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-24T06:44:50.000Z","uid":40152,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"59630188fc8f8a683b896d24aabcc4b22c2d2c96","tid":2122672,"uid":40152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T06:35:09.000Z","msg":"水務署今日表示，該署屯門濾水廠内進行工程的一名承建商工人確診2019冠狀病毒病。事件對食水安全沒有影響。<br />\n<br />\n該名承建商工人最近一次上班日期為昨日（七月二十三日）。他昨晚獲通知確診，目前已入院接受隔離治療，情況穩定。<br />\n<br />\n該名承建商工人工作時有佩戴口罩，於上班期間一直有進行體溫探測，體溫正常。水務署已即時安排全面清潔及消毒屯門濾水廠，並會與衞生防護中心保持緊密聯繫，亦已提醒所有人員須注意個人衞生，並時刻提高警覺。如發現身體不適，必須馬上求醫。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1828044/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E6%B0%B4%E5%8B%99%E7%BD%B2%E4%B8%80%E5%90%8D%E6%89%BF%E5%BB%BA%E5%95%86%E5%B7%A5%E4%BA%BA%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA-%E5%B1%AF%E9%96%80%E6%BF%BE%E6%B0%B4%E5%BB%A0%E5%85%A8%E9%9D%A2%E6%B6%88%E6%AF%92\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1828044%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E5%258B%2599%25E7%25BD%25B2%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%2590%258D%25E6%2589%25BF%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E5%2595%2586%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E8%25A8%25BA-%25E5%25B1%25AF%25E9%2596%2580%25E6%25BF%25BE%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E5%25BB%25A0%25E5%2585%25A8%25E9%259D%25A2%25E6%25B6%2588%25E6%25AF%2592&d=7JJHJI7m8dwGfBTVwC1i6E2FGjryiJR74P7%2B0uEOyUg%3D&h=d35f2ae0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1828044%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E5%258B%2599%25E7%25BD%25B2%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%2590%258D%25E6%2589%25BF%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E5%2595%2586%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E8%25A8%25BA-%25E5%25B1%25AF%25E9%2596%2580%25E6%25BF%25BE%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E5%25BB%25A0%25E5%2585%25A8%25E9%259D%25A2%25E6%25B6%2588%25E6%25AF%2592&h=8e4300eb\" target=\"_blank\"